# Locked Obsidian Depth (3D shell)

Canonical: [`.context/locked-obsidian-depth.md`](../../.context/locked-obsidian-depth.md) · [`docs/design/themes/OBSIDIAN-DEPTH-SPEC.md`](../../docs/design/themes/OBSIDIAN-DEPTH-SPEC.md)

## MUST

- Preserve glassmorphism + tactile 3D on `.od-depth__bento-card`, `.od-depth__cta`, `.od-depth__dock`
- Selection chrome (pills/mode-select): Ethereal Blue `#7BA3C9` utan yttre glow (Pontus 2026-07-24)
- Guld kvar på `.od-depth__cta` + dock/kompass — ingen guldig bloom på kategori-val
- Run `npm run smoke:obsidian-depth` when touching locked files
- Route `/dev/obsidian-depth` stays available as canonical reference

## MUST NOT

- Remove or flatten Obsidian Depth to plain calm-card without product OK
- Delete `obsidian-depth-*.png` kanon images or mockup page without registry update
- Change `OD-obsidian-depth` theme pack without updating `VARIANTS.md`
- Återinföra guldig glow på `.od-depth__pill--active` / mode-select

## Separate work (allowed)

Refine prod buttons, drawer menu, Fyren dock, header chrome — without replacing the locked OD bento/shell spec.
